      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "we require a significant storage + risk of serving stale data.\nbut we avoid making call to profile service on runtime.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "we require a significant storage + risk of serving stale data.\nbut we avoid making call to profile service on runtime.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "GLke4bRZLNX_QPdrn5l6X",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1645.8652405203002,
      "y": 33190.09727610817,
      "width": 847,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bIn",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1122384469,
      "version": 92,
      "versionNonce": 1861780117,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775786986998,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "In either case, you should never store feed of a user is \"list\" (say mongoDB)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "In either case, you should never store feed of a user is \"list\" (say mongoDB)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "-ePEtsHDC6HQM3Dq1-qtT",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1665.8481980414153,
      "y": 33237.41551799853,
      "width": 506,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bIo",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 607588949,
      "version": 159,
      "versionNonce": 2039943867,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775786965321,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- it will bloat up document size on mongoDB.\n- expensive serialization and deserialization.\n- iteration is difficult.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- it will bloat up document size on mongoDB.\n- expensive serialization and deserialization.\n- iteration is difficult.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "WcUx6KMxzFS4PCmaw_K64",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1616.2468354388059,
      "y": 33362.693290150135,
      "width": 297,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bIp",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 580675515,
      "version": 136,
      "versionNonce": 1584913717,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775787148753,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Hence we go with Approach 1\nwe can use DynamoDB",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Hence we go with Approach 1\nwe can use DynamoDB",
