      "updated": 1775840746632,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- WHen A registers a \"swipe\" for B.\n- A should need see B again in the feed.\n- while generating the feed, we have to check\nfor past swipe & add only if new.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- WHen A registers a \"swipe\" for B.\n- A should need see B again in the feed.\n- while generating the feed, we have to check\nfor past swipe & add only if new.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
